        {
            "title": "羅啟豪善心爆棚再辦市集推留港消費  復活節義賣首飾望突破6位數",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"羅啟豪善心爆棚再辦市集  復活節好去處義賣首飾以突破6位數善款為目標\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/6cbd2d84bc536823667a4b9fcafc5d62/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250415/_2025041512413325414.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">羅啟豪善心爆棚再辦市集  復活節好去處義賣首飾以突破6位數善款為目標</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>去年聖誕，羅啟豪的歌迷會「豪吧」舉辦「羅啟豪冬日約會迷你市集」取得成功，既能共襄善舉，又積極支持社企發展，市民與遊客可以超筍價購得心頭好，一舉多得。早前啟豪代表「豪吧」領取「卓越支持社企機構大獎」，他承諾未來與歌迷繼續行善，關懷社會。言出必行，為期六天（4月18至21日及26至27日）的《上水廣場 X 羅啟豪 分享歌單·音樂營地市集》接力登場，節目內容豐富，揭幕當日（4月18日） 同場上演【羅啟豪分享歌單·音樂會】在，是復活節好去處。\n\n</p><h2>復活節行市集</h2>\n<p>演唱會有part 2，羅啟豪歌迷會「豪吧」一手策劃的市集都有part 2，由冬日玩到春日，令啟豪始料不及：「去年市集確實很成功，當再次收到合作邀約，我和一班『豪殼』（歌迷暱稱）感到相當驚喜，要在短時間之內籌備一個全新市集，存在一定挑戰與考驗。」迎難而上，圍繞啟豪新歌《還未分享的歌單》作市集主題，構思出驚喜內容，啟豪推介：「今次《羅啟豪 分享歌單·音樂營地約會》將移師戶外舉行，營造露營風，為與大家分享我的音樂，晴空區域會搭建巨型帳篷，以兩米投影機播放我出道以來的演出片段；市集着重食買玩，我們搜羅了不少筍貨供大家選購，又設有多個有獎遊戲攤位，成功完成任務便可免費享用手工烘焙及精美凍飲，務求令大家盡興而歸。」市集揭幕日（18日），啟豪同場舉辦音樂會，歌迷耳福不淺，也有機會獲贈紀念匙扣及啟豪親筆簽名Tee等精美禮品。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196071/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"本月18日舉行《羅啟豪 分享歌單·音樂營地市集》。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b26dae4d6156a0b0dea5d372fafdad00/2025-04/JAC10978.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        本月18日舉行《羅啟豪 分享歌單·音樂營地市集》。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196095/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"羅啟豪上月出席「十分關懷 良心消費運動2024」頒獎禮，代表其歌迷會「豪吧」領取最高級別的「卓越支持社企機構大獎」，首次有歌迷會獲此項殊榮，成為娛樂圈創舉。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b28ca2ff847a8277b065fd2cd17b70eb/2025-04/09_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        羅啟豪上月出席「十分關懷 良心消費運動2024」頒獎禮，代表其歌迷會「豪吧」領取最高級別的「卓越支持社企機構大獎」，首次有歌迷會獲此項殊榮，成為娛樂圈創舉。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196072/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"市集出售多家本地社企特色產品，羅啟豪開幕首日仲會唱歌。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/385d4293e73f34d21c633bdee957ad26/2025-04/JAC11017.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        市集出售多家本地社企特色產品，羅啟豪開幕首日仲會唱歌。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196073/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"市集活動首日，羅啟豪舉行音樂會。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/248506e7c007583b55f80278212b4d12/2025-04/JAC11052.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        市集活動首日，羅啟豪舉行音樂會。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196074/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"復活節，支持留港消費！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ea876c2134fbc6fc8601eb665ccc3f52/2025-04/JAC11103.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        復活節，支持留港消費！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196075/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"市集音樂會，另有啟豪二手首飾義賣，善款悉數捐贈慈善機構。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d523ffe3dbbafbe07af15a076a0cbed8/2025-04/JAC11115.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        市集音樂會，另有啟豪二手首飾義賣，善款悉數捐贈慈善機構。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196076/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"市集活動首日，羅啟豪同場舉行音樂會。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2efd8e748c900dd2440f1db5d845dad9/2025-04/JAC11124.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        市集活動首日，羅啟豪同場舉行音樂會。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196077/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"市集活動首日，羅啟豪同場舉行音樂會。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/533e79061cd7a8b7137c9ba4ed2dc46f/2025-04/JAC11130.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        市集活動首日，羅啟豪同場舉行音樂會。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196078/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"市集有嘢買有歌聽，是復活節好去處。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/26af9d1b9773bcb8782b8a99f701d173/2025-04/LN_busking_website_icon_1080x1080px_aw01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        市集有嘢買有歌聽，是復活節好去處。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196079/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"羅啟豪籲留港消費！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e740a0fc911375ad8da891423f25ee90/2025-04/PR_pic_2_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        羅啟豪籲留港消費！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196080/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"市集出售多家本地社企的食品、飲品等。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c36b29a8a391b157b79dc6f6da4b162a/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-14_at_1_17_46_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        市集出售多家本地社企的食品、飲品等。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196081/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"市集出售多家本地社企特色產品。肚餓呀！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7909184ecddacc1b8907ea1cdde79e91/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-14_at_1_17_46_PM_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        市集出售多家本地社企特色產品。肚餓呀！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4196082/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"市集出售多家本地社企特色產品。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2ff509a69eefc0c931572d3e553e82b4/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-14_at_1_17_46_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        市集出售多家本地社企特色產品。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>羅啟豪為善最樂</h2>\n<p>延續啟豪積極行善的初心，市集繼續出售多家本地社企特色產品，現場更有啟豪的二手首飾義賣，善款悉數捐贈慈善機構，啟豪說：「上次『聖誕市集』義賣我的二手衫，反應非常熱烈，這次我再挑選了一批首飾義賣，每件都陪伴過我一同完成滿懷回憶的難忘演出，很有紀念與收藏價值，希望大家踴躍競投。」他心目中有沒有善款目標數字？「『聖誕市集』籌到接近六位數字，我當然期望今次能突破六位，多多益善。」\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
